OL,3,C40 years of Nissan: The deal that
OL,4,Cchanged Wearside
OL,6,FIt has been 40 years since the
OL,7,Fdecision was made to bring Nissan to
OL,8,FWearside: making Sunderland a giant in
OL,9,Fcar manufacturing, and changing the
OL,10,Fcourse of the lives of local workers
OL,11,Fand the local economy.
OL,13,FA small team had worked on the project
OL,14,Fto secure Nissan for three years,
OL,15,Fsuccessfully bringing the biggest
OL,16,Fforeign investment of its kind in the
OL,17,Fregion.
