OL,3,C40 years of Nissan: The deal that
OL,4,Cchanged Wearside
OL,6,FThe news came on 30 March 1984, in an
OL,7,Fearly morning call to the offices of
OL,8,FWashington Development Corporation.
OL,9,FThe call was answered by Ed Robson and
OL,10,Fquickly passed the news to Geoff Key,
OL,11,FGed Parker and the team who had worked
OL,12,Ffor three years to attract Nissan.
OL,14,FIt ended months of speculation, with
OL,15,FWearside, Wales and the then-named
OL,16,FHumberside battling to be the chosen
OL,17,Fsite.
