OL,3,C40 years of Nissan: The deal that
OL,4,Cchanged Wearside
OL,6,FEdwin Robson, former Chief Planning
OL,7,FOfficer, said: "We were being pursued
OL,8,Fby reporters saying have they made a
OL,9,Fdecision, do you know? We didn't know.
OL,10,FEverybody claimed to know, we didn't
OL,11,Fknow, I wish we had it would have
OL,12,Fsaved a lot of heartache."
