OL,3,C40 years of Nissan: The deal that
OL,4,Cchanged Wearside
OL,6,FEx-Sunderland Borough Council Chief
OL,7,FExecutive, Geoff Key said: "Tyne Tees
OL,8,Fand others were saying this is going
OL,9,Fto Wales. So I slept quite well,
OL,10,Fthinking that's it, I haven't got
OL,11,Ftomorrow to worry about, we've got a
OL,12,Fpress conference, I'll just look
OL,13,Fmiserable. But, thankfully, next day I
OL,14,Fget a phone call from Ed."
OL,16,FMr Robson added that following the
OL,17,Fcall: "It was yabba dabba doo!"
