OL,3,C40 years of Nissan: The deal that
OL,4,Cchanged Wearside
OL,6,FCharles Slater, the former leader of
OL,7,FSunderland Borough Council, announced
OL,8,Fthe news that generations of industry
OL,9,Fon Wearside were about to changeJOn
OL,10,F30th March 1984, he said: "It's a shot
OL,11,Fin the arm. It's a gesture of
OL,12,Fconfidence in the North East, for too
OL,13,Flong, for too long the people south of
OL,14,Fthe wash as it were have viewed this
OL,15,Farea as a backwater."
