OL,3,C40 years of Nissan: The deal that
OL,4,Cchanged Wearside
OL,6,FAs Nissan executives flew in to
OL,7,FNewcastle airport to confirm the deal,
OL,8,Fthe news spread.JGed Parker, a former
OL,9,Fsenior research officer at Washington
OL,10,FDevelopment Corporation, recalled the
OL,11,Foverwhelming confirmation that jobs
OL,12,Fand prosperity were on the horizon:
OL,13,F"The talk in the pubs! A teacher
OL,14,Ffriend told me, the headteacher had
OL,15,Fgone around every class and told them
OL,16,Fthat Nissan were coming. It was just a
OL,17,Fbuzz."
