OL,3,C40 years of Nissan: The deal that
OL,4,Cchanged Wearside
OL,6,FThe announcement came with the promise
OL,7,Fof new jobs at the plant plus an
OL,8,Festimated 4000 more in the local area
OL,9,Fas a knock-on effect. At the time,
OL,10,FWearside was an area where one in four
OL,11,Fmen were unemployed.
OL,13,FIn fact, in 1984, unemployment reached
OL,14,Fa peak of nearly 3.3 million people
OL,15,Fout of work.JWhen Nissan first started
OL,16,Fto advertise roles in Sunderland,
OL,17,Flocal job centres were reporting a
OL,18,Fflood of applications from as far away
OL,19,Fas Cornwall.
