OL,3,C40 years of Nissan: The deal that
OL,4,Cchanged Wearside
OL,6,FWhen the plant first opened, 470
OL,7,Fpeople were employed. The number has
OL,8,Fnow swelled to 6000 direct employees
OL,9,Fand around 30,000 more in the supply
OL,10,Fchain.
OL,12,FThe airfield that was commissioned to
OL,13,Fbe transformed into the site looked
OL,14,Fincredibly different four decades ago.
OL,15,FIt would go on to, quite literally,
OL,16,Fchange the landscape of Wearside.
OL,18,FIt was two years until the factory
OL,19,Fopened and the first car to drive off
OL,20,Fthe production line was a Bluebird.
