OL,3,C40 years of Nissan: The deal that
OL,4,Cchanged Wearside
OL,6,FIt marked the start of an industry
OL,7,Fthat has now supported many thousands
OL,8,Fof jobs, families and livelihoods in
OL,9,Fthe region.
OL,11,FThe North East Chamber of Commerce
OL,12,Freflected on the impact the site has
OL,13,Fmade on the area. Chief Executive,
OL,14,FJohn McCabe said: "Nissan being here
OL,15,Fin the North East has really shown
OL,16,Fwhat we're capable of as a region, we
OL,17,Fcan build big industries, we can build
OL,18,Fsupply chains around them, we can take
OL,19,Fbig investment in our region and
OL,20,Freally develop a fantastic economy
OL,21,Faround that.
