OL,6,F"So, Nissan has helped us really raise
OL,7,Four aspirations and look to the future
OL,8,Fto see what can be possible for this
OL,9,Ffantastic region."
OL,11,FGateshead College now trains 1,500
OL,12,Fstudents on engineering and automotive
OL,13,Fcourses in state-of-the-art facilities.
