OL,3,C40 years of Nissan: The deal that
OL,4,Cchanged Wearside
OL,6,FLast year, 100% of the students went
OL,7,Fon to work in the field or moved into
OL,8,Ffurther education.J"I feel confident
OL,9,Fthat I can find work in this area and
OL,10,FI can work around the same area, which
OL,11,Fmeans I don't have to relocate, which
OL,12,Fis better", students told ITV Tyne
OL,13,FTees.
OL,15,F"With Nissan and their giga-factories
OL,16,Fopening, I feel like there are loads
OL,17,Fof well-paid opportunities and jobs."
