OL,3,C40 years of Nissan: The deal that
OL,4,Cchanged Wearside
OL,6,FThe principal of Gateshead College,
OL,7,FDavid Alexander, said Nissan's
OL,8,Fpresence in the region cannot be
OL,9,Funderestimated: "It's been a real
OL,10,Fsuccess story for the North East and
OL,11,Fits impact on our local economy and
OL,12,Fthe employment opportunities it's
OL,13,Fprovided have been significant.
OL,15,F"So, as a college and as a sector we
OL,16,Fcontinue to invest heavily to make
OL,17,Fsure that people get the opportunity
OL,18,Fto take up those employments with
OL,19,FNissan and with the supply chain."
